---
import BaseSection from '@components/BaseSection.astro'
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
---

<BaseSection class="bg-white rounded-3xl text-black">
  <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.5rem,8vw,9rem)] mb-4">About me.</h2>

  <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-between gap-10">
    <Image
      class="w-full h-full"
      src="/damn-ice-cube.gif"
      alt="me"
      width="600"
      height="600"
    />
    <div class="text-[clamp(1rem,5vw,2rem)]">
      <p>
        My journey in this field has been an exhilarating one, marked by
        continuous learning and a deep commitment to creating exceptional user
        experiences.
      </p>
      <p>
        Throughout my career, I've had the privilege of working on a diverse
        range of projects, from e-commerce platforms to interactive web
        applications.
      </p>
      <p>
        My primary focus has always been on crafting clean, intuitive, and
        visually appealing user interfaces. I take pride in my ability to
        transform complex ideas into elegant, user-friendly designs.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseSection>
